metadata.name: Bozzo 0001 - Boris Johnson
metadata.description: With “get Brexit done” as his slogan, Boris Johnson led his party to a landslide election victory. The Consumer Prices Index in the UK including owner occupiers' housing costs rose by 9.6% in the 12 months to October 2022, up from 8.8% in September 2022.

attributes.value: Former Primer Minister of the UK
